2654435761); h2 = Math.imul(h2 ^ ch, 1597334677); } h1 = Math.imul(h1 ^ (h1>>>16), 2246822507) ^ Math.imul(h2 ^ (h2>>>13), 3266489909); h2 = Math.imul(h2 ^ (h2>>>16), 2246822507) ^ Math.imul(h1 ^ (h1>>>13), 3266489909); return 4294967296 * (2097151 & h2) + (h1>>>0); }; // Hash Function Credits: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/7616461/generate-a-hash-from-string-in-javascript function
